o<toolchange> sub

(MSG, Vymen nastroj a stiskni Cycle Start)

G53 G0 Z-5
G53 G0 X10 Y10

M0

( pozice sondy )
G53 G0 X23 Y44

( probing )
G91
G38.2 Z-50 F200
G0 Z2
G38.2 Z-5 F20
G90

#<touch_z> = #5063
#<probe_ref> = -150
#<tool_length> = [#<probe_ref> - #<touch_z>]

G10 L1 P#<_selected_tool> Z#<tool_length>

G53 G0 Z0

o<toolchange> endsub
M2